  Added: xsquad.is_permanent_squad -- static identity guard (story, trader, named_npc, empty), cached
  Added: xsquad.has_active_role -- dynamic role guard (task_giver, companion)
  Added: MCM banner
  Removed: xsquad.is_unscriptable_squad -- replaced by is_permanent_squad + has_active_role
